---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy & Cookie Policy — Monster Roller Budapest">
  <div class="privacy-wrap">
    <aside class="privacy-toc" aria-label="Privacy contents navigation">
      <p class="privacy-toc-label">Contents</p>
      <nav class="privacy-toc-links">
        <a href="#overview" data-section-link="overview">Overview</a>
        <a href="#who-we-are" data-section-link="who-we-are">Who We Are</a>
        <a href="#data-we-collect" data-section-link="data-we-collect">Data We Collect</a>
        <a href="#how-we-use-it" data-section-link="how-we-use-it">How We Use It</a>
        <a href="#sharing" data-section-link="sharing">Sharing Your Data</a>
        <a href="#cookies" data-section-link="cookies">Cookies</a>
        <a href="#your-rights" data-section-link="your-rights">Your Rights</a>
        <a href="#contact-us" data-section-link="contact-us">Contact Us</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <main class="privacy-content">
      <header class="privacy-hero">
        <p class="privacy-eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1>Privacy & Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="privacy-meta">Last updated: March 2025 · Monster Roller Budapest</p>
        <p class="privacy-intro">This policy explains what personal data we collect when you use the Monster Roller Budapest website, how we use it, and what rights you have. We keep it simple because we respect your time.</p>
        <div class="privacy-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </header>

      <section id="overview" class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">Overview</h2>
        <p class="animate-on-scroll">Monster Roller Budapest operates the website monsterrollerbp.com. This privacy policy describes the personal data collected when you use our website and booking services, how that data is used and protected, and what choices you have. By using our website you agree to the practices described here.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="who-we-are" class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">Who We Are</h2>
        <p class="animate-on-scroll">The data controller responsible for your personal data is Monster Roller Budapest, operating from Haris köz 2, 1052 Budapest, Hungary. You can reach us at bpsegway@gmail.com or by phone at +36 30 258 4709. We are a small team - your data is handled by us directly, not by a large corporation.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="data-we-collect" class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">Data We Collect</h2>
        <p class="animate-on-scroll">When you make a booking or contact us via our website or WhatsApp, we collect your name, email address, phone number, and the details of your booking request including date, number of participants, and any special notes you provide. We do not collect payment information directly - payments are handled in person on the day of your tour.</p>
        <h3>Automatically collected data</h3>
        <p>When you visit our website, standard technical data is automatically collected by your browser including your IP address, browser type and version, the pages you visit, and the time and date of your visit. This data is used only for site performance and security purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="how-we-use-it" class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p class="animate-on-scroll">We use your personal data solely to respond to your booking requests and inquiries, to confirm and manage your reservation, and to contact you with relevant information about your tour. We do not use your data for advertising, we do not sell it to third parties, and we do not send unsolicited marketing emails. If you give us your contact details, we use them only to communicate with you about your booking.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="sharing" class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">Sharing Your Data</h2>
        <p class="animate-on-scroll">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes. Your data may be shared only in the following limited cases: with our own team members who need it to fulfill your booking, with service providers who operate our website infrastructure such as hosting and analytics providers, or when required by Hungarian or EU law such as a court order or regulatory request.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="cookies" class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="animate-on-scroll">Our website uses cookies - small text files stored on your device - to make the site function correctly and to understand how visitors use it. We use three types of cookies:</p>
        <h3>Essential cookies</h3>
        <p>These are required for basic website functionality such as remembering your preferences within a session. The site cannot function properly without them.</p>
        <h3>Performance cookies</h3>
        <p>These help us understand how visitors use the site - which pages are most visited, how long people stay, and where they come from. This helps us improve the site. No personally identifiable information is stored.</p>
        <h3>Third-party cookies</h3>
        <p>Some third-party services we use - such as Google Maps embedded on our contact page - may set their own cookies. These are governed by the privacy policies of those third parties. You can control cookie settings through your browser at any time.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="your-rights" class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="animate-on-scroll">Under GDPR and Hungarian data protection law, you have the right to access the personal data we hold about you, to request a correction if it is inaccurate, to request deletion of your data at any time, to withdraw any consent you have given, and to object to certain types of processing. To exercise any of these rights simply contact us at bpsegway@gmail.com and we will respond within 30 days.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="contact-us" class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="animate-on-scroll">If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your data, please get in touch. We are a small team and we take privacy seriously.</p>
        <div class="privacy-contact-card">
          <div class="privacy-contact-row">
            <span>Email</span>
            <a href="mailto:bpsegway@gmail.com">bpsegway@gmail.com</a>
          </div>
          <div class="privacy-contact-row">
            <span>Phone</span>
            <a href="tel:+36302584709">+36 30 258 4709</a>
          </div>
          <div class="privacy-contact-row">
            <span>Address</span>
            <p>Haris köz 2, 1052 Budapest</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="privacy-bottom-nav">
        <a href="/" class="privacy-ghost-btn">← Back to Home</a>
        <a href="/tours" class="privacy-ghost-btn">View All Tours →</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const sections = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.privacy-section'));
      const tocLinks = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[data-section-link]'));

      const setActiveTocLink = (id) => {
        tocLinks.forEach((link) => {
          const isActive = link.getAttribute('data-section-link') === id;
          link.classList.toggle('active', isActive);
        });
      };

      tocLinks.forEach((link) => {
        link.addEventListener('click', (event) => {
          event.preventDefault();
          const targetId = link.getAttribute('data-section-link');
          const targetSection = targetId ? document.getElementById(targetId) : null;
          if (!targetSection) return;
          targetSection.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
        });
      });

      if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
        const sectionObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
          entries.forEach((entry) => {
            if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;
            setActiveTocLink(entry.target.id);
          });
        }, {
          rootMargin: '-30% 0px -55% 0px',
          threshold: 0.05,
        });

        sections.forEach((section) => sectionObserver.observe(section));
      } else {
        if (sections[0]) {
          setActiveTocLink(sections[0].id);
        }
      }
    });
  </script>

  <style>
    :global(html) {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    .privacy-wrap {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 120px 60px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 220px minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 80px;
    }

    .privacy-toc {
      position: sticky;
      top: 100px;
      height: max-content;
    }

    .privacy-toc-label {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: #f97316;
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .privacy-toc-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .privacy-toc-links a {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 8px 0 8px 12px;
      border-left: 2px solid transparent;
      transition: color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .privacy-toc-links a:hover {
      border-left-color: #f97316;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .privacy-toc-links a.active {
      border-left-color: #f97316;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .privacy-content {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .privacy-eyebrow {
      margin: 0;
      color: #f97316;
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .privacy-hero h1 {
      margin: 14px 0 10px;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 52px;
      line-height: 1.04;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .privacy-meta {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    }

    .privacy-intro {
      margin: 20px 0 0;
      max-width: 760px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .privacy-divider {
      width: 100%;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      margin: 40px 0;
    }

    .privacy-section {
      margin-bottom: 64px;
      scroll-margin-top: 110px;
    }

    .privacy-section h2 {
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      border-left: 3px solid #f97316;
      padding-left: 16px;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .privacy-section p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .privacy-section h3 {
      margin: 20px 0 8px;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .privacy-section h3 + p {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .privacy-section p + h3,
    .privacy-section p + p,
    .privacy-section .privacy-contact-card {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .privacy-contact-card {
      background: #111111;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
      padding: 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .privacy-contact-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .privacy-contact-row span {
      color: #f97316;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .privacy-contact-row a,
    .privacy-contact-row p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      font-size: 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .privacy-contact-row a:hover {
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .privacy-bottom-nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      padding-top: 6px;
    }

    .privacy-ghost-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 40px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.45);
      color: #f97316;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      background: transparent;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .privacy-ghost-btn:hover {
      background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .animate-on-scroll {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(18px);
      transition: opacity 0.55s ease, transform 0.55s ease;
    }

    .animate-on-scroll.is-visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-toc-links a {
      color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.55);
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-toc-links a:hover,
    :global(html.light) .privacy-toc-links a.active {
      color: #111827;
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-hero h1,
    :global(html.light) .privacy-section h2,
    :global(html.light) .privacy-section h3 {
      color: #111827;
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-meta {
      color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.5);
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-intro,
    :global(html.light) .privacy-section p {
      color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-divider {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-contact-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-contact-row a,
    :global(html.light) .privacy-contact-row p {
      color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.78);
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-contact-row a:hover {
      color: #111827;
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-ghost-btn {
      border-color: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.5);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    }

    :global(html.light) .privacy-ghost-btn:hover {
      background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.12);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .privacy-wrap {
        padding: 80px 24px;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 0;
      }

      .privacy-toc {
        display: none;
      }

      .privacy-hero h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
      }

      .privacy-section h2 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .privacy-bottom-nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .privacy-ghost-btn {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .privacy-contact-row {
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 6px;
      }

      .privacy-contact-row a,
      .privacy-contact-row p {
        text-align: left;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>